  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Unmatched Performance",
      "text": "The CRS326-4C+20G+2Q+RM is the ultimate network switch for demanding environments. Boasting 20x 2.5 Gigabit Ethernet ports, 4x combo ports (2.5 Gigabit Ethernet or 10G SFP+), and 2x 40G QSFP+ ports, it delivers unparalleled density and ultra-fast fiber connectivity. The CRS326-4C+20G+2Q+RM is the ideal choice for demanding networks seeking an affordable solution with exceptional port density, speed, and advanced features. Upgrade your network performance and enjoy the flexibility to adapt to ever-changing needs."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Built for Reliability",
      "text": "This powerhouse switch doesn't compromise on reliability. The CRS326-4C+20G+2Q+RM features a massive heatsink and two powerful fans, ensuring cool operation even under heavy loads. Dual-redundant power supplies ensure uptime, while an extra 100 Mbps Ethernet management port provides dedicated control. The included rackmount ears and fastening set make it easy to integrate into your infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Advanced Features",
      "text": "The CRS326-4C+20G+2Q+RM goes beyond a simple switch, offering a powerful combination of hardware and software features to empower demanding network environments with flexibility, performance, and advanced functionalities. The powerful Marvell Prestera switch-chip delivers exceptional performance and scalability, ensuring smooth operation even under demanding workloads. While the dedicated CPU powers the switch, guaranteeing efficient handling of complex tasks like traffic management, advanced configurations, and Layer 3 routing."
    }
  ],
